{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"abf999006f","title":"毛泽东在苏共中央给南共中央的信上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6d4c695242","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":15,"articleId":"abf999006f"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1422f82c25","type":"title","text":"毛泽东在苏共中央给南共中央的信上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abf999006f"},{"id":"f511b23858","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abf999006f"},{"id":"887f6d1d71","type":"paragraph","text":"苏共五月九日给南共的信，是一个好文件，和我们的立场完全一致。他们想通了，站起来了。请你做两件事：(一)找苏使馆负责人谈一下，表示热忱祝贺。或者在大会后由我找他谈一次。这是一件大事，苏共政治理论有转机，作风在改，大有希望。(二)将苏件立即印发大会代表阅读。如有时间在小组会上谈论一次，并可带回去。奇文互相赏，迅即印发。此信附印在苏件上，放在前面。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abf999006f"},{"id":"af609346c0","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东五月十五日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abf999006f"}],"page":{"id":"4e6d4177c5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"abf999006f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}